  "description": "Certificate of Lawfulness (Existing) for a loft conversion to include a rear dormer, the conversion of roof from hip to gabled end and two front roof lights.",
  "decision_conditions": [
    "The operations do not fall within the provisions of Schedule 2, Part 1, Class B of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) Order 2015 as limited under provision (B2)(a) and (B2)(aa)(bb);",
    "I) The material used for the exterior of the side gable is not similar to those used in the construction of the exterior of the existing house",
    "II) The eaves of the original roof is not re-instated and",
    "III) The edge of the enlargement closest to the eaves of the original roof is less than 20 centimetres from the eaves measured along the roof slope from the outside edge of the eaves.",
    "As a result, it is considered that the loft conversion including a hip to gable roof alteration with a rear dormer window to be retained is not permitted development.",
    "Informative:",
    "It is noted that the pre-existing front elevation with the gabled roof form is inaccurate; as the original roof form is hipped."
